<br>
Look like it as a soccer team.<br>
Some players you like and can get along with, while some others can be real nice to you but complete jerks to others.<br>
<br>
A guild is usually a place where the people in the guild get along with each other and like each others opinions and so on.<br>
But in dealing with other people's persons views might not be the same.<br>
<br>
I consider just about everyone on this server as my friend or a friend that I dont know yet.<br>
I don't care one bit about that guildtag over there head, since the few people that I dont like have all had diffrent guildtags.<br>
<br>
I am sure there are people who thinks people in Landslide are creeps some dont even like me. I like everyone in my guild, there is not one I would want to lose.<br>
<br>
As for Tides of Valor, I don't know many people from that guild since most of them play at very diffrent times then us. So far no one in Tides has been rude to me, but a few has helped me when I have been in trouble.<br>
<br>
Get angry at people, not at what team they are on.<br>
