<br>
The thing about Tides is:<br>
<br>
Some guilds have some real talented and outgoing players that contribute to the community at whole, which in turn make their guild stand out and shine. Tides, on the other hand, harbors people whose past speaks for its self. They are the people that ninja looted your quest piece, stole your camp, Kill stole the NPC you waited on all day, pulled that huge train etc etc. Their merry band of full time assholes eclipse any decent members they might have. Its to the point that we almost expect this kind of bullshit behavior from a any Tides member, and thus, we all have writen them a blank check.<br>
<br>
Every server has a guild like Tides. The High School crowd tends to seek each other out and form these Wanna Be kewl dewds white trash, suburban gagstah type guilds who only care about getting &quot;da phat lewts&quot; by any means possible short of stealing it off their own grandmother. They probably get a narrow amount of respect from those that care only about the ability to take down &quot;UberMOB XYZ&quot;, but otherwise, they are mainly just a bunch of punks.<br>
